      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person! I have absolutely babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible, spotless shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up. It's been kept tucked away in a garage and has been meticulously cared for, so it\u2019s basically like getting a brand-new ride without the brand-new price tag. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
