    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a genuine time capsule, meticulously preserved to a standard that exceeds original showroom expectations. The exterior paintwork is breathtaking, retaining a deep, mirror-like factory luster absolutely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel alignment is precise, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather seating shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior retains its original, clean scent. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, operate with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a spotless engine bay and a comprehensive, documented service history that confirms its pampered life. On the road, the ride is tight, silent, and powerful, offering the exact performance profile of a brand-new machine. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example.",
